HEADWORD: Water rail
<hw>Wa"ter rail`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of
numerous species of rails of the genus <gen>Rallus</gen>, as the common
European species (<spn>Rallus aquaticus</spn>). See <xex>Illust.</xex>
of <er>Rail</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

